@use 'design-system/assets/sass/import/import-core' as *;

// -------
// COMPONENT STYLE
// -------

/*
  The Button component styles are located in this file
  (./projects/design-system/assets/sass/utils/helpers/_buttons.scss).
  Because this component is also used in the CMS via rich text,
  these button styles are compiled and minified into common.css and
  are included on every page of the app from the <head> section.
*/
:host {
    display: inline-flex;
